ar\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/United_States_dollar\\\">US$<\\/a>1\\u00a0billion in annual sales, becoming the fastest retailer in history to do so. Apple has expanded the number of retail locations and its geographical coverage over the years, with 522 stores across 25 countries and regions worldwide, opening its newest store at American Dream Mall in East Rutherford, New Jersey on December 3, 2022.<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-2\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2px;\\\"><a style=\\\"color: #3366cc; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Apple_Store#cite_note-2\\\">[2]<\\/a><\\/sup><sup id=\\\"cite_ref-3\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2px;\\\"><a style=\\\"color: #3366cc; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Apple_Store#cite_note-3\\\">[3]<\\/a><\\/sup>\\u00a0Strong product sales have placed Apple among the top-tier retail stores, with sales over $16\\u00a0billion globally in 2011.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#593030\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
