the preferred choice of customers. Personally, I have known about the brand for the longest time. It was the only makeup brand I knew that was used by people around me\\u2026my mother and elder sister. So when it came for my time to choose a brand for myself, it was quite straightforward and simple,\\u201d she said.<\\/p>\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"d59e74e\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\",\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_color\":\"#FBEDEDCF\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9fc042b\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8d9706a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>At Lakm\\u00e9 Salon, with over 35 years of experience, and a footprint of over 400+ Lakm\\u00e9 Salons in 125 cities across the length and breadth of the country, we have developed a deep understanding of the beauty industry, its professionals and the skills needed to make a mark. More than 280 entrepreneurs have partnered with Lakm\\u00e9 Lever as franchisees to own and operate Lakm\\u00e9 Salons across the country<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1e11b5c\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"e900230\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/Screenshot-from-2023-03-26-18-34-32.png\",\"id\":57,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_element_width\":\"inherit\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
