\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/07\\/timeline-19_2.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"story-img wp-post-image\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/07\\/timeline-19_2.jpg\\\" sizes=\\\"100vw\\\" alt=\\\"2017\\\" width=\\\"188\\\" height=\\\"139\\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"content-details\\\">\\n<p class=\\\"p1\\\"><span class=\\\"s1\\\">The most spectacular blondes with\\u00a0<b>k.blonde<\\/b>: k.blonde Bleaching Clay and k.blonde Bleaching cream ammonia-free make it possible to customize the most desired shades of blonde.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"clt-2018\\\" class=\\\"timeline-year scrollable-section \\\" data-section-title=\\\"2018\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"icon-placeholder\\\"><span class=\\\"ctl-timeline-date\\\">2018<\\/span><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-bar\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"story-7288\\\" class=\\\"timeline-post odd light-grey-post icons_no  default-skin\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-content clearfix ctlvisible animated\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"ctl_info event-description full\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"full-width\\\"><a class=\\\"ctl_prettyPhoto\\\" title=\\\"2018\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/07\\/timeline-20.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"story-img wp-post-image\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/07\\/timeline-20.jpg\\\" sizes=\\\"100vw\\\" alt=\\\"2018\\\" width=\\\"184\\\" height=\\\"241\\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"content-details\\\">CHROMA, reinventing color. It is formulated with the exclusive OF5 molecule, a revolutionary technology in hair coloring. The first molecule capable of delaying the oxidation of dyes.<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"story-7290\\\" class=\\\"timeline-post even light-grey-post icons_no  default-skin\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-content clearfix ctlvisible animated\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"ctl_info event-description full\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"full-width\\\"><a class=\\\"ctl_prettyPhoto\\\" title=\\\"2018\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/07\\/timeline-21.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"story-img wp-post-image\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/07\\/timeline-21.jpg\\\" sizes=\\\"100vw\\\" alt=\\\"2018\\\" width=\\\"168\\\" height=\\\"201\\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"content-details\\\">AURA, the first biotechnological hair treatment formulated with organic ingredients that straightens and softens the hair fiber and eliminates frizz.<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"clt-2019\\\" class=\\\"timeline-year scrollable-section \\\" data-section-title=\\\"2019\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"icon-placeholder\\\"><span class=\\\"ctl-timeline-date\\\">2019<\\/span><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-bar\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"story-7292\\\" class=\\\"timeline-post odd light-grey-post icons_no  default-skin\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-content clearfix ctlvisible animated full-visible\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"ctl_info event-description full\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"full-width\\\"><a class=\\\"ctl_prettyPhoto\\\" title=\\\"2019\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/07\\/timeline-22-1.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"story-img wp-post-image\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/07\\/timeline-22-1.jpg\\\" sizes=\\\"100vw\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/07\\/timeline-22-1.jpg 300w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/07\\/timeline-22-1-215x300.jpg 215w\\\" alt=\\\"2019\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"419\\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"content-details\\\">TEKNIA is the fusion of experience, innovation and inspiration: the best beauty ritual for nourished, healthy and eternally beautiful hair.<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"clt-2021\\\" class=\\\"timeline-year scrollable-section \\\" data-section-title=\\\"2021\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"icon-placeholder\\\"><span class=\\\"ctl-timeline-date\\\">2021<\\/span><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-bar\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"story-9713\\\" class=\\\"timeline-post even light-grey-post icons_no  default-skin\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-content clearfix ctlvisible animated full-visible\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"ctl_info event-description full\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"full-width\\\"><a class=\\\"ctl_prettyPhoto\\\" title=\\\"2021\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/07\\/reshaping-color.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"story-img wp-post-image\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/07\\/reshaping-color.jpg\\\" sizes=\\\"100vw\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/07\\/reshaping-color.jpg 900w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/07\\/reshaping-color-300x250.jpg 300w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/07\\/reshaping-color-768x640.jpg 768w\\\" alt=\\\"2021\\\" width=\\\"525\\\" height=\\\"438\\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"content-details\\\">Lakm\\u00e9 creates the integrated color system. Collage is evolving, but its flagship formula remain intact. Gloss, the ammonia-free, demipermanent, strengthens haircare and exclusively partners with Collage to achieve an integrated Lakm\\u00e9 color system.<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"clt-2022\\\" class=\\\"timeline-year scrollable-section \\\" data-section-title=\\\"2022\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"icon-placeholder\\\"><span class=\\\"ctl-timeline-date\\\">2022<\\/span><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-bar\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"story-11073\\\" class=\\\"timeline-post odd light-grey-post icons_no  default-skin\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-content clearfix ctlvisible animated full-visible\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"ctl_info event-description full\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"full-width\\\"><a class=\\\"ctl_prettyPhoto\\\" title=\\\"2022\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/04\\/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"story-img wp-post-image\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/04\\/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-1024x1024.jpg\\\" sizes=\\\"100vw\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/04\\/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/04\\/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/04\\/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/04\\/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/04\\/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-250x250.jpg 250w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/04\\/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-180x180.jpg 180w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/04\\/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/04\\/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-100x100.jpg 100w\\\" alt=\\\"2022\\\" width=\\\"525\\\" height=\\\"525\\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"content-details\\\">\\n<p class=\\\"xxmsonormal\\\">LAKM\\u00c9 is expanding the universe of TEKNIA.<\\/p>\\n<p class=\\\"xxmsonormal\\\"><b>TEKNIA SCALP CARE<\\/b>\\u00a0is an avant-garde line of products designed to treat the root problem in order to protect, soothe, nourish, and rebalance the scalp.<\\/p>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"clt-2023\\\" class=\\\"timeline-year scrollable-section \\\" data-section-title=\\\"2023\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"icon-placeholder\\\"><span class=\\\"ctl-timeline-date\\\">2023<\\/span><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-bar\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"story-13653\\\" class=\\\"timeline-post even light-grey-post icons_no  default-skin\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-content clearfix ctlvisible animated full-visible\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"ctl_info event-description full\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"full-width\\\"><a class=\\\"ctl_prettyPhoto\\\" title=\\\"2023\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB.png\\\"><img class=\\\"story-img wp-post-image\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-1024x1024.png\\\" sizes=\\\"100vw\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-1024x1024.png 1024w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-150x150.png 150w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-300x300.png 300w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-768x768.png 768w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-250x250.png 250w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-180x180.png 180w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-600x600.png 600w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-100x100.png 100w\\\" alt=\\\"2023\\\" width=\\\"525\\\" height=\\\"525\\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"content-details\\\"><strong>k.blonde<\\/strong>, \\\"The ultimate protection for blondes\\\" and\\u00a0<strong>K2.0<\\/strong>, \\\"At the top of restoring hair\\\". Two launches that, combined, achieve optimum performance.<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div>\\u00a0<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div>\\u00a0<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
