(272, 72, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"5aaa1745\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"109c80fa\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b7e4ecc\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"fce8b47\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9baed76\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"272098b\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/12345.jpg\",\"id\":55,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"35f01ac\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"268d499\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"fe6ce74\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Nehru quickly approached industrialist Jehangir Ratanji Dadabhoy Tata for a solution and Lakm\\u00e9 was introduced as India\\u2019s first homegrown cosmetics brand in 1952. It was a\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.tatacentralarchives.com\\/tata-legacy\\/lakmes-history.html\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\">subsidiary<\\/a>\\u00a0of Tata Oil Mills, a company originally tasked with crushing copra for exporting coconut oil.<\\/p>\\n<p>The name Lakme is a French word for goddess Lakshmi, known for her beauty in mythology. This was suggested by the brand\\u2019s French collaborators, Robert Piguet and Renoir. Lakme was a popular opera in France by L\\u00e9o Delibes, named after its protagonist who was inspired by the Indian goddess.<\\/p>\\n<p>Lakme was groundbreaking for the Indian market because it offered cosmetics suitable for Indian skin types, for which extensive research was\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.researchgate.net\\/publication\\/349463522_A_Comprehensive_Analysis_of_Top_Indian_Cosmetic_Company_LAKME\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\">carried out<\\/a>.The brand got a\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/corporatecitizen.in\\/v2-issue3\\/corporate-history-lakme-was-nehrus-idea.html\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\">makeover<\\/a>\\u00a0when Dadabhoy\\u2019s Swiss wife Simone Tata took over as its managing director in 1961. From pricing of products to the brand\\u2019s positioning, she made it a household name. Simone became the company\\u2019s chairperson in 1982.<img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/Screenshot-from-2023-03-26-18-03-11.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"320\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Go-to brand<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<p>\\u201cI never knew Lakm\\u00e9 was an Indian brand. I always thought it was European. And it was affordable too, so I always liked to buy them during my college days. But the reason for my preference was also because it was everywhere. It was advertised in the newspapers, TV and all my favorite actors were in it. I still use some of its products,\\u201d said 44-year old Seema Rana, a teacher at a Delhi school.<\\/p>\\n<p>Dolly Sharma, also a Delhi resident, had similar reasons for liking Lakm\\u00e9 products over others.<\\/p>\\n<p>\\u201cMy husband runs a pharmacy. Lakm\\u00e9 brings us the most revenue because it is the preferred choice of customers. Personally, I have known about the brand for the longest time. It was the only makeup brand I knew that was used by people around me\\u2026my mother and elder sister. So when it came for my time to choose a brand for myself, it was quite straightforward and simple,\\u201d she said.<\\/p>\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"d59e74e\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\",\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_color\":\"#FBEDEDCF\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9fc042b\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8d9706a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>At Lakm\\u00e9 Salon, with over 35 years of experience, and a footprint of over 400+ Lakm\\u00e9 Salons in 125 cities across the length and breadth of the country, we have developed a deep understanding of the beauty industry, its professionals and the skills needed to make a mark. More than 280 entrepreneurs have partnered with Lakm\\u00e9 Lever as franchisees to own and operate Lakm\\u00e9 Salons across the country<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1e11b5c\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"e900230\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/Screenshot-from-2023-03-26-18-34-32.png\",\"id\":57,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_element_width\":\"inherit\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"4280d32\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7d55d71\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"987fbe9\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>\\u201cIn 1996, Lakm\\u00e9 was captured in an image for the first time. The first snapshot to mark the beginning of the brand\'s journey.\\u201d<\\/p>\\n<div id=\\\"story-4186\\\" class=\\\"timeline-post odd light-grey-post icons_no  default-skin\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-content clearfix ctlvisible animated\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"ctl_info event-description full\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"content-details\\\">Lakm\\u00e9 wins its first European distribution agreements at the COSMOPROF WORLDWIDE fair in Bologna.<\\/div>\\n<div>The brand wins its first distribution agreements in Taiwan, Hong Kong, Malaysia and Australia at the COSMOPROF ASIA fair.<\\/div>\\n<div>\\n<div id=\\\"story-4183\\\" class=\\\"timeline-post even light-grey-post icons_no  default-skin large\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-content clearfix ctlvisible animated\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"ctl_info event-description full\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"content-details\\\">Relaunching of Collage permanent coloring and expansion of the collection\\u2019s shades.<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"clt-2002\\\" class=\\\"timeline-year scrollable-section \\\" data-section-title=\\\"2002\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"icon-placeholder\\\"><span class=\\\"ctl-timeline-date\\\">2002<\\/span><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-bar\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"story-4182\\\" class=\\\"timeline-post odd light-grey-post icons_no  default-skin\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-content clearfix ctlvisible animated full-visible\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"ctl_info event-description full\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"full-width\\\"><a class=\\\"ctl_prettyPhoto\\\" title=\\\"2002\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timeline-6.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"story-img wp-post-image\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timeline-6.jpg\\\" sizes=\\\"100vw\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timeline-6.jpg 200w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timeline-6-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timeline-6-180x180.jpg 180w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timeline-6-100x100.jpg 100w\\\" alt=\\\"Lakme 2002\\\" width=\\\"200\\\" height=\\\"200\\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"content-details\\\">Inauguration of the company\\u2019s new facilities in Sant Just Desvern.<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"clt-2003\\\" class=\\\"timeline-year scrollable-section \\\" data-section-title=\\\"2003\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"icon-placeholder\\\"><span class=\\\"ctl-timeline-date\\\">2003<\\/span><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-bar\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"story-4181\\\" class=\\\"timeline-post even light-grey-post icons_no  default-skin\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-content clearfix ctlvisible animated\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"ctl_info event-description full\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"full-width\\\"><a class=\\\"ctl_prettyPhoto\\\" title=\\\"2003\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timeline-7.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"story-img wp-post-image\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timeline-7.jpg\\\" sizes=\\\"100vw\\\" alt=\\\"Lakme 2003\\\" width=\\\"202\\\" height=\\\"254\\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"content-details\\\">Lakm\\u00e9 achieves its first distributors in North America at the COSMORPROF NORTH AMERICA fair.<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"clt-2004\\\" class=\\\"timeline-year scrollable-section \\\" data-section-title=\\\"2004\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"icon-placeholder\\\"><span class=\\\"ctl-timeline-date\\\">2004<\\/span><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-bar\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"story-4180\\\" class=\\\"timeline-post odd light-grey-post icons_no  default-skin\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-content clearfix ctlvisible animated full-visible\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"ctl_info event-description full\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"full-width\\\"><a class=\\\"ctl_prettyPhoto\\\" title=\\\"2004\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timeline-8.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"story-img wp-post-image\\\" sr