ated full-visible\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"ctl_info event-description full\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"full-width\\\"><a class=\\\"ctl_prettyPhoto\\\" title=\\\"2008\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timeline-11.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"story-img wp-post-image\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timeline-11.jpg\\\" sizes=\\\"100vw\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timeline-11.jpg 200w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timeline-11-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timeline-11-180x180.jpg 180w, https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timeline-11-100x100.jpg 100w\\\" alt=\\\"Lakme 2008\\\" width=\\\"200\\\" height=\\\"200\\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"content-details\\\">Reformulation of k.style, the line of finishing products that create lasting volume, shine, texture and extreme finishes.<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"clt-2009\\\" class=\\\"timeline-year scrollable-section \\\" data-section-title=\\\"2009\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"icon-placeholder\\\"><span class=\\\"ctl-timeline-date\\\">2009<\\/span><\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-bar\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"story-4176\\\" class=\\\"timeline-post odd light-grey-post icons_no  default-skin large\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"timeline-content clearfix ctlvisible animated full-visible\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"ctl_info event-description full\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"content-details\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2359\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/lakme.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timeline-12.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"457\\\" height=\\\"172\\\" \\/><\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"clt-2010\\\" class=\\\"timeline-year scrollable-section \\\" data-section-title=\\\"2010\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"icon-placeholder\\\"><span class=\\\"ctl-timeline-dat