 French collaborators, Robert Piguet and Renoir. Lakme was a popular opera in France by L\\u00e9o Delibes, named after its protagonist who was inspired by the Indian goddess.<\\/p><p>Lakme was groundbreaking for the Indian market because it offered cosmetics suitable for Indian skin types, for which extensive research was\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.researchgate.net\\/publication\\/349463522_A_Comprehensive_Analysis_of_Top_Indian_Cosmetic_Company_LAKME\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\">carried out<\\/a>.The brand got a\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/corporatecitizen.in\\/v2-issue3\\/corporate-history-lakme-was-nehrus-idea.html\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\">makeover<\\/a>\\u00a0when Dadabhoy\\u2019s Swiss wife Simone Tata took over as its managing director in 1961. From pricing of products to the brand\\u2019s positioning, she made it a household name. Simone became the company\\u2019s chairperson in 1982.<\\/p><p><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/Screenshot-from-2023-03-26-18-03-11.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"320\\\" height=\\\"320\\\" \\/><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Go-to brand<\\/span><\\/p><p>\\u201cI never knew Lakm\\u00e9 was an Indian brand. I always thought it was European. And it was affordable too, so I always liked to buy them during my college days. But the reason for my preference was also because it was everywhere. It was advertised in the newspapers, TV and all my favorite actors were in it. I still use some of its products,\\u201d said 44-year old Seema Rana, a teacher at a Delhi school.<\\/p><p>Dolly Sharma, also a Delhi resident, had similar reasons for liking Lakm\\u00e9 products over others.<\\/p><p>\\u201cMy husband runs a pharmacy. Lakm\\u00e9 brings us the most revenue because it is the preferred choice of customers. Personally, I have known about the brand for the longest time. It was the only makeup brand I knew that was used by people around me\\u2026my mother and elder sister. So when it came for my time to choose a brand for myself, it was quite straightforward and simple,\\u201d she said.<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"d59e74e\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\",\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_color\":\"#FBEDEDCF\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9fc042b\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8d9706a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>At Lakm\\u00e9 Salon, with over 35 years of experience, and a footprint of over 400+ Lakm\\u00e9 Salons in 125 cities across the length and breadth of the country, we have developed a deep understanding of the beauty industry, its professionals and the skills needed to make a mark. More than 280 entrepreneurs have partnered with Lakm\\u00e9 Lever as franchisees to own and operate Lakm\\u00e9 Salons across the country<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1e11b5c\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"e900230\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/Screenshot-from-2023-03-26-18-34-32.png\",\"id\":57,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_element_width\":\"inherit\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"4280d32\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7d55d71\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"987fbe9\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"ee99653\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9958277\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f5cc969\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Welcome to Lakm\\u00e9, the beauty destination that inspires women all over the world to express their unique beauty. Our vision is to make every woman feel confident, radiant, and empowered through our premium beauty products.<\\/p><p>For over 60 years, Lakm\\u00e9 has been a trusted brand in the beauty industry, with a focus on innovation, quality, and inclusivity. Our collection of skincare, makeup, and haircare products is carefully curated to cater to all your beauty needs, from everyday essentials to special occasions.<\\/p><p>Skincare<\\/p><p>We believe that beautiful makeup starts with healthy skin. That\'s why our skincare range is specially formulated to nourish, protect, and enhance your natural beauty. From gentle cleansers to hydrating moisturizers, our collection offers a variety of products for every skin type and concern. Our best-selling Absolute Perfect Radiance range is a fan-favorite, enriched with real gold micro particles to give you a radiant, glowing complexion.<\\/p><p>Makeup<\\/p><p>At Lakm\\u00e9, we believe that makeup is an art form that can transform your look and boost your confidence. Our makeup range is designed to help you create any look you desire, whether it\'s a natural no-makeup makeup look or a bold, statement look. Our collection includes lipsticks, foundations, eyeshadows, mascaras, and more, in a variety of shades and finishes to suit every skin tone and type. Our signature product, the Lakm\\u00e9 Absolute Argan Oil Serum Foundation, is a cult favorite, providing buildable coverage with a dewy finish that lasts all day.<\\/p><p>Haircare<\\/p><p>Good hair days are a must for any beauty routine, and our haircare range is specially formulated to help you achieve your dream hair. From nourishing shampoos and conditioners to hair masks and styling products, our collection offers everything you need to keep your locks healthy, shiny, and manageable. Our bestselling 9to5 Primer + Matte Lip Color is an everyday essential for any makeup bag.<\\/p><p>Collections<\\/p><p>Looking for inspiration? Our curated collections offer the latest beauty trends and timeless classics for every occasion. From bridal makeup to festive looks, our collections make it easy to find the perfect products to help you look and feel your best.<\\/p><p>Shop with Confidence<\\/p><p>At Lakm\\u00e9, we believe in providing our customers with the best shopping experience. Our online store is easy to use, and we offer a variety of payment options, including cash on delivery. Plus, we offer free shipping on all orders over [insert amount]. With our 100% satisfaction guarantee, you can shop with confidence knowing that you\'re getting the best products and service.<\\/p><p>Join our Community<\\/p><p>Connect with other beauty enthusiasts and get inspired by our community of Lakm\\u00e9 lovers. Follow us on social media to stay up to date on the latest trends, tips, and products. Join our loyalty program to earn rewards and exclusive offers.<\\/p><p>Experience the Beauty of Lakm\\u00e9<\\/p><p>At Lakm\\u00e9, we believe that beauty is not just about looking good, but also feeling good. Our premium beauty products are designed to enhance your natural beauty and make you feel confident and empowered. Explore our collection today and discover the beauty of Lakm\\u00e9.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"8eeecc9\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"163f15b\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"115a8de\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>\\u201cIn 1996, Lakm\\u00e9 was captured in an image for the first time. The first snapshot to mark the beginning of the brand\'s journey.\\u201d<br \\/>Lakm\\u00e9 wins its first European distribution agreements at the COSMOPROF WORLDWIDE fair in Bologna.<br \\/>The brand wins its first distribution agreements in Taiwan, Hong Kong, Malaysia and Australia at the COSMOPROF ASIA fair.<br \\/>Relaunching of Collage permanent coloring and expansion of the collection\\u2019s shades.<br \\/>2002<br \\/>Inauguration of the company\\u2019s new facilities in Sant Just Desvern.<br \\/>2003<br \\/>Lakm\\u00e9 achieves its first distributors in North America at the COSMORPROF NORTH AMERICA fair.<br \\/>2004<br \\/>The brand is now present in more than 65 countries and Lakm\\u00e9 becomes and international hairdressing hub.<br \\/>2006<br \\/>Reformulation of the ammonia-free, semi-permanent Gloss coloring collection and launching of new shades.<br \\/>2007<br \\/>Relaunching of k.therapy, the wellness and health treatment for hair and scalp.<br \\/>2008<br \\/>Reformulation of k.style, the line of finishing products that create lasting volume, shine, texture and extreme finishes.<br \\/>2009<br \\/>2010<br \\/>Relaunching TEKNIA, Lakm\\u00e9\\u2019s high-tech line designed to hydrate and care for all hair types<br \\/>2012<br \\/>Launching of Collage+, permanent coloring that provides maximum color intensity and gray coverage.<br \\/>2013<br \\/>Launching of CHROMA, Lakm\\u00e9\\u2019s ammonia-free permanent coloring.<br \\/>2014<br \\/>Launching of k.style COOL, the trendiest finishing products to create unique looks.<br \\/>2015<br \\/>Inauguration of the company\\u2019s new facilities.<br \\/>2016<br \\/>Lakm\\u00e9 defies the passage of time with i.plex: an anti-aging treatment that fights the aging process of hair.<br \\/>2017<br \\/>The most spectacular blondes with k.blonde: k.blonde Bleaching Clay and k.blonde Bleaching cream ammonia-free make it possible to customize the most desired shades of blonde.<br \\/>2018 <br \\/>CHROMA, reinventing color. It is formulated with the exclusive OF5 molecule, a revolutionary technology in hair coloring. The first molecule capable of delaying the oxidation of dyes.<br \\/>AURA, the first biotechnological hair treatment formulated with organic ingredients that straightens and softens the hair fiber and eliminates frizz.<br \\/>2019<br \\/>TEKNIA is the fusion of experience, innovation and inspiration: the best beauty ritual for nourished, healthy and eternally beautiful hair.<br \\/>2021<br \\/>Lakm\\u00e9 creates the integrated color system. Collage is evolving, but its flagship formula remain intact. Gloss, the ammonia-free, demipermanent, strengthens haircare and exclusively partners with Collage to achieve an integrated Lakm\\u00e9 color system.<br \\/>2022<br \\/>LAKM\\u00c9 is expanding the universe of TEKNIA.<br \\/>TEKNIA SCALP CARE is an avant-garde line of products designed to treat the root problem in order to protect, soothe, nourish, and rebalance the scalp.<br \\/>2023<br \\/>k.blonde, \\\"The ultimate protection for blondes\\\" and K2.0, \\\"At the top of restoring hair\\\". Two launches that, combined, achieve optimum performance.<br \\/><br \\/><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"d015b2f\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b3a508e\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"54a1061\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/123556.jpeg\",\"id\":69,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1c5f899\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":