ry technology in hair coloring. The first molecule capable of delaying the oxidation of dyes.<br>AURA, the first biotechnological hair treatment formulated with organic ingredients that straightens and softens the hair fiber and eliminates frizz.<br>TEKNIA is the fusion of experience, innovation and inspiration: the best beauty ritual for nourished, healthy and eternally beautiful hair.<br>Lakm\\u00e9 creates the integrated color system. Collage is evolving, but its flagship formula remain intact. Gloss, the ammonia-free, demipermanent, strengthens haircare and exclusively partners with Collage to achieve an integrated Lakm\\u00e9 color system.<br>LAKM\\u00c9 is expanding the universe of TEKNIA.<br>TEKNIA SCALP CARE is an avant-garde line of products designed to treat the root problem in order to protect, soothe, nourish, and rebalance the scalp.<br>k.blonde, \\\"The ultimate protection for blondes\\\" and K2.0, \\\"At the top of restoring hair\\\". Two launches that, combined, achieve optimum performance.<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"left\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"d015b2f\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b3a508e\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"54a1061\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/123556.jpeg\",\"id\":69,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1c5f899\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"52d0a55\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"736076c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/35678.jpeg