ze\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"115a8de\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>\\u201cIn 1996, Lakm\\u00e9 was captured in an image for the first time. The first snapshot to mark the beginning of the brand\'s journey.\\u201d<br>Lakm\\u00e9 wins its first European distribution agreements at the COSMOPROF WORLDWIDE fair in Bologna.<br>The brand wins its first distribution agreements in Taiwan, Hong Kong, Malaysia and Australia at the COSMOPROF ASIA fair.<br>Relaunching of Collage permanent coloring and expansion of the collection\\u2019s shades.<br>Inauguration of the company\\u2019s new facilities in Sant Just Desvern.<br>Lakm\\u00e9 achieves its first distributors in North America at the COSMORPROF NORTH AMERICA fair.<br>The brand is now present in more than 65 countries and Lakm\\u00e9 becomes and international hairdressing hub.<br>Reformulation of the ammonia-free, semi-permanent Gloss coloring collection and launching of new shades.<br>Relaunching of k.therapy, the wellness and health treatment for hair and scalp Reformulation of k.style, the line of finishing products that create lasting volume, shine, texture and extreme finishes. Relaunching TEKNIA, Lakm\\u00e9\\u2019s high-tech line designed to hydrate and care for all hair types<br>Launching of Collage+, permanent coloring that provides maximum color intensity and gray coverage.<br>Launching of CHROMA, Lakm\\u00e9\\u2019s ammonia-free permanent coloring.<br>Launching of k.style COOL, the trendiest finishing products to create unique looks.<br>Inauguration of the company\\u2019s new facilities. Lakm\\u00e9 defies the passage of time with i.plex: an anti-aging treatment that fights the aging process of hair. The most spectacular blondes with k.blonde: k.blonde Bleaching Clay and k.blonde Bleaching cream ammonia-free make it possible to customize the most desired shades of blonde.<br>CHROMA, reinventing color. It is formulated with the exclusive OF5 molecule, a revolutionary technology in hair coloring. The first molecule capable of delaying the oxidation of dyes.<br>AURA, the first biotechnological hair treatment formulated with organic ingredients that straightens and softens the hair fiber and eliminates frizz.<br>TEKNIA is the fusion of experience, innovation and inspiration: the best beauty ritual for nourished, healthy and eternally beautiful hair.<br>Lakm\\u00e9 creates the integrated color system. Collage is evolving, but its flagship formula remain intact. Gloss, the ammonia-free, demipermanent, strengthens haircare and exclusively partners with Collage to achieve an integrated Lakm\\u00e9 color system.<br>LAKM\\u00c9 is expanding the universe of TEKNIA.<br>TEKNIA SCALP CARE is an avant-garde line of products designed to treat the root problem in order to protect, soothe, nourish, and rebalance the scalp.<br>k.blonde, \\\"The ultimate protection for blondes\\\" and K2.0, \\\"At the top of restoring hair\\\". Two launches that, combined, achieve optimum performance.<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"left\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"d015b2f\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b3a508e\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"54a1061\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/123556.jpeg\",\"id\":69,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1c5f899\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"52d0a55\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"736076c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/35678.jpeg