(824, 53, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"f5593e9\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c99abc0\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"10dca6c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p style=\\\"border-style: solid; border-color: #d9d9e3; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 1.25em; color: #374151; font-family: S\\u00f6hne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #f7f7f8;\\\">Our Mission: Our mission at Lakme is to inspire and empower women to feel confident and beautiful in their own skin. We are committed to delivering the best possible beauty products that are tailored to meet the diverse needs of women across India. Our aim is to provide our customers with an exceptional beauty experience that enhances their natural beauty and boosts their self-confidence.<\\/p><p style=\\\"border-style: solid; border-color: #d9d9e3; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 1.25em; color: #374151; font-family: S\\u00f6hne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #f7f7f8;\\\">Our Values: At Lakme, we value innovation, quality, diversity, and sustainability. We are always exploring new and innovative ways to create products that cater to the diverse needs of women in India. We are committed to using only the finest and most sustainable ingredients in our products to ensure that we leave the smallest possible carbon footprint. We celebrate diversity and inclusivity in everything we do, and strive to create a welcoming and empowering environment for all our employees, customers, and partners.<\\/p><p style=\\\"border-style: solid; border-color: #d9d9e3; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 1.25em; color: #374151; font-family: S\\u00f6hne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #f7f7f8;\\\">Our Legacy: Lakme\'s legacy is one of innovation and excellence. Over the past 50 years, we have introduced numerous groundbreaking products and technologies that have revolutionized the beauty industry in India. Our pioneering spirit has made us one of the most trusted and well-loved beauty brands in the country, and we are proud to have played a part in empowering millions of women across India.<\\/p><p style=\\\"border-style: solid; border-color: #d9d9e3; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 1.25em; color: #374151; font-family: S\\u00f6hne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #f7f7f8;\\\">Our Team: Our team at Lakme is made up of some of the most talented and passionate professionals in the beauty industry. From product development to marketing, sales to customer service, every member of our team is dedicated to delivering the best possible beauty experience to our customers. We believe in nurturing talent and providing opportunities for growth and development, and are proud to have a diverse and inclusive team that reflects the values and aspirations of our brand.<\\/p><p style=\\\"border-style: solid; border-color: #d9d9e3; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #374151; font-family: S\\u00f6hne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #f7f7f8;\\\">Thank you for taking the time to learn more about Lakme. We hope that our passion for beauty and commitment to excellence comes through in everything we do, and that you will join us on our journey to empower women and celebrate the beauty of diversity in India.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"54a48c3\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b78c964\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9c71b94\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/lkm.jpeg\",\"id\":152,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"aca816a\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9544f1e\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/lk2.jpeg\",\"id\":151,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"f966d56\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f7422d1\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"bf076c8\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 12pt;\\\">Welcome to Lakme, a leading cosmetics brand in India that has been empowering women for over 50 years. Our journey began in 1952, when we launched the first-ever beauty salon in India, and since then, we have been committed to delivering high-quality and innovative beauty products that enhance the natural beauty of women.<\\/span><br><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 12pt;\\\">At Lakme, we believe that beauty is not just about external appearances, but also about inner confidence and self-esteem. Our products are designed to help women feel confident and beautiful from within, by enhancing their natural features and complementing their unique personalities<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_element_width\":\"inherit\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1a1405f\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"aafff46\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/css.jpeg\",\"id\":154,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"f9939f3\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"dacb630\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9f54387\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/ssss.jpeg\",\"id\":155,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"e367734\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c5d3f30\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>From skincare to makeup, haircare to fragrances, our products are crafted using the latest technologies and the finest ingredients, to provide the best possible results for our customers. Our product range caters to every skin type, age, and occasion, and is constantly evolving to meet the ever-changing needs of women.<br \\/><br \\/><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"f1d1d6e\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a92f675\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ce862e4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>We are also committed to sustainability and social responsibility, and have implemented various initiatives to reduce our carbon footprint and support the communities we operate in. We believe in giving back to society and have partnered with various organizations to promote education, health, and environmental awareness.<br \\/>Thank you for choosing Lakme as your beauty partner. We are dedicated to providing you with the best possible beauty experience and look forward to continuing to empower women for many more years to come.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"d9e116f\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a6472ee\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/1342w34r5.jpeg\",\"id\":156,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"0802a58\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"da05a17\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9250af9\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\\\">Our Product Range: At Lakme, we offer a wide range of beauty products that cater to every skin type, age, and occasion. Our skincare range includes products for cleansing, toning, moisturizing, and treating various skin concerns, such as acne, dark spots, and aging. Our makeup range includes products for face, eyes, lips, and nails, and is designed to enhance and highlight the natural features of every woman. We also offer arange of haircare products, including shampoos, conditioners, and styling products, as well as fragrances that cater to every mood and personality.\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/span>\\n\\n<span style=\\\"background-color: var(--base-3); color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight );\\\">Our Innovation: Innovation is at the heart of everything we do at Lakme. We are constantly exploring new and innovative ways to create products that meet the ever-changing needs and preferences of our customers. Our research and development team is dedicated to developing new and cutting-edge technologies that are tailored to the unique demands of the Indian market. We are also committed to ensuring that all our products are safe and effective, and go through rigorous testing before they are launched.<\\/span>\\n\\n<span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\\\">Our Partnerships: At Lakme, we believe in the power of partnerships. We work closely with various organizations and individuals to promote sustainability, social responsibility, and women\'s empowerment. We have partnered with NGOs and charities to support education, healthcare, and environmental initiatives across India. We also collaborate with fashion designers and influencers to bring the latest trends and styles to our customers.<\\/span>\\n\\n<span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\\\">Our Customer Service: At Lakme, we are committed to providing our customers with the best possible beauty experience. We understand that every customer is unique, and we strive to provide personalized and attentive service to each and every one of them. Our customer service team is always available to answer any questions or concerns that our customers may have, and we are constantly seeking feedback and suggestions to improve our products and services.<\\/span>\\n\\n<span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\\\">We hope that this additional content helps provide a comprehensive overview of Lakme and what makes us unique. We are dedicated to empowering women and celebrating their natural beauty, and we look forward to continuing to innovate and create products that meet the diverse needs of our customers.<\\/span>\",\"align\":\"justify\",\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"40725c8\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"e6471dc\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b77e13a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\\\">Our Product Range: At Lakme, we offer a wide range of beauty products that cater to every skin type, age, and occasion. Our skincare range includes products for cleansing, toning, moisturizing, and treating various skin concerns, such as acne, dark spots, and aging. Our makeup range includes products for face, eyes, lips, and nails, and is designed to enhance and highlight the natural features of every woman. We also offer a range of haircare products, including shampoos, conditioners, and styling products, as well as fragrances that cater to every mood and personality.<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\\\">Our Innovation: Innovation is at the heart of everything we do at Lakme. We are constantly exploring new and innovative ways to create products that meet the ever-changing needs and preferences of our customers. Our research and development team is dedicated to developing new and cutting-edge technologies that are tailored to the unique demands of the Indian market. We are also committed to ensuring that all our products are safe and effective, and go through rigorous testing before they are launched.<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\\\">Our Partnerships: At Lakme, we believe in the power of partnerships. We work closely with various organizations and individuals to promote sustainability, social responsibility, and women\'s empowerment. We have partnered with NGOs and charities to support education, healthcare, and environmental initiatives across India. We also collaborate with fashion designers and influencers to bring the latest trends and styles to our customers.<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\\\">Our Customer Service: At Lakme, we are committed to providing our customers with the best possible beauty experience. We understand that every customer is unique, and we strive to provide personalized and attentive service to each and every one of them. Our customer service team is always available to answer any questions or concerns that our customers may have, and we are constantly seeking feedback and suggestions to improve our products and services.<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\\\">We hope that this additional content helps provide a comprehensive overview of Lakme and what makes us unique. We are dedicated to empowering women and celebrating their natural beauty, and we look forward to continuing to innovate and create products that meet the diverse needs of our customers.<\\/span><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"67819da\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b8387ec\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f8a8c39\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<div class=\\\"group w-full text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 border-b border-black\\/10 dark:border-gray-900\\/50 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-[#444654]\\\"><div class=\\\"text-base gap-4 md:gap-6 md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-2xl xl:max-w-3xl p-4 md:py-6 flex lg:px-0 m-auto\\\"><div class=\\\"relative flex w-[calc(100%-50px)] flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3 lg:w-[calc(100%-115px)]\\\"><div class=\\\"flex flex-grow flex-col gap-3\\\"><div class=\\\"min-h-[20px] flex flex-col items-start gap-4 whitespace-pre-wrap\\\"><div class=\\\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\\\"><p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'comic sans ms\', sans-serif;\\\">Our Salons: In addition to our range of beauty products, Lakme also operates a network of salons across India. Our salons offer a wide range of services, including haircuts, hair color, styling, makeup, skincare, and more. Our trained professionals are committed to delivering high-quality services that meet the unique needs and preferences of our customers. We also offer bridal packages that are tailored to make every bride look and feel her best on her special day.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'comic sans ms\', sans-serif;\\\">Our Awards and Recognition: Over the years, Lakme has been recognized with numerous awards and accolades for our contributions to the beauty industry. We have been awarded the Best Make-Up Brand award by Femina magazine for several consecutive years, and have been recognized by various industry bodies for our innovative products and sustainable practices. We are proud to have received such recognition, which is a testament to our commitment to excellence and innovation.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'comic sans ms\', sans-serif;\\\">Our Social Media Presence: At Lakme, we believe in the power of social media to connect with our customers and inspire them to feel confident and beautiful. We maintain an active presence on various social media platforms, including Instagram, Facebook, and YouTube, where we share makeup tutorials, beauty tips, product launches, and more. We also run various social media campaigns and contests to engage with our customers and provide them with a fun and interactive beauty experience.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'comic sans ms\', sans-serif;\\\">Our Future: At Lakme, we are always looking towards the future and exploring new and exciting ways to innovate and grow. We are committed to expanding our product range, launching new salons, and strengthening our partnerships with various organizations and individuals to promote sustainability and women\'s empowerment. We are also exploring new technologies, such as augmented reality and artificial intelligence, to provide our customers with an even more personalized and engaging beauty experience.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'comic sans ms\', sans-serif;\\\">We hope that this additional detail provides a deeper understanding of what Lakme stands for and what our future aspirations are. We are passionate about empowering women and celebrating their natural beauty, and we look forward to continuing to do so for many years to come.<\\/span><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><\\/div><div class=\\\"flex justify-between\\\"><div class=\\\"text-gray-400 flex self-end lg:self-center justify-center mt-2 gap-3 md:gap-4 lg:gap-1 lg:absolute lg:top-0 lg:translate-x-full lg:right-0 lg:mt-0 lg:pl-2 visible\\\" style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div><\\/div><\\/div><\\/div><\\/div>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
