tion\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f7422d1\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"bf076c8\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 12pt;\\\">Welcome to Lakme, a leading cosmetics brand in India that has been empowering women for over 50 years. Our journey began in 1952, when we launched the first-ever beauty salon in India, and since then, we have been committed to delivering high-quality and innovative beauty products that enhance the natural beauty of women.<\\/span><br><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 12pt;\\\">At Lakme, we believe that beauty is not just about external appearances, but also about inner confidence and self-esteem. Our products are designed to help women feel confident and beautiful from within, by enhancing their natural features and complementing their unique personalities<\\/span><br><\\/p>\",\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_element_width\":\"inherit\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1a1405f\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"aafff46\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/css.jpeg\",\"id\":154,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"f9939f3\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"dacb630\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9f54387\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/ssss.jpeg\",\"id\":155,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"e367734\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c5d3f30\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>From skincare to makeup, haircare to fragrances, our products are crafted using the latest technologies and the finest ingredients, to provide the best possible results for our customers. Our product range caters to every skin type, age, and occasion, and is constantly evolving to meet the ever-changing needs of women.<br \\/><br \\/><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"f1d1d6e\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a92f675\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ce862e4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>We are also committed to sustainability and social responsibility, and have implemented various initiatives to reduce our carbon footprint and support the communities we operate in. We believe in giving back to society and have partnered with various organizations to promote education, health, and environmental awareness.<br \\/>Thank you for choosing Lakme as your beauty partner. We are dedicated to providing you with the best possible beauty experience and look forward to continuing to empower women for many more years to come.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"d9e116f\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a6472ee\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/1342w34r5.jpeg\",\"id\":156,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"0802a58\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"da05a17\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9250af9\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\\\">Our Product Range: At Lakme, we offer a wide range of beauty products that cater to every skin type, age, and occasion. Our skincare range includes products for cleansing, toning, moisturizing, and treating various skin concerns, such as acne, dark spots, and aging. Our makeup range includes products for face, eyes, lips, and nails, and is designed to enhance and highlight the natural features of every woman. We also offer arange of haircare products, including shampoos, conditioners, and styling products, as well as fragrances that cater to every mood and personality.\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/span>