><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\\\">Our Partnerships: At Lakme, we believe in the power of partnerships. We work closely with various organizations and individuals to promote sustainability, social responsibility, and women\'s empowerment. We have partnered with NGOs and charities to support education, healthcare, and environmental initiatives across India. We also collaborate with fashion designers and influencers to bring the latest trends and styles to our customers.<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\\\">Our Customer Service: At Lakme, we are committed to providing our customers with the best possible beauty experience. We understand that every customer is unique, and we strive to provide personalized and attentive service to each and every one of them. Our customer service team is always available to answer any questions or concerns that our customers may have, and we are constantly seeking feedback and suggestions to improve our products and services.<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\\\">We hope that this additional content helps provide a comprehensive overview of Lakme and what makes us unique. We are dedicated to empowering women and celebrating their natural beauty, and we look forward to continuing to innovate and create products that meet the diverse needs of our customers.<\\/span><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"67819da\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b8387ec\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f8a8c39\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<div class=\\\"group w-full text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 border-b border-black\\/10 dark:border-gray-900\\/50 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-[#444654]\\\"><div class=\\\"text-base gap-4 md:gap-6 md:max-w