e also run various social media campaigns and contests to engage with our customers and provide them with a fun and interactive beauty experience.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'comic sans ms\', sans-serif;\\\">Our Future: At Lakme, we are always looking towards the future and exploring new and exciting ways to innovate and grow. We are committed to expanding our product range, launching new salons, and strengthening our partnerships with various organizations and individuals to promote sustainability and women\'s empowerment. We are also exploring new technologies, such as augmented reality and artificial intelligence, to provide our customers with an even more personalized and engaging beauty experience.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'comic sans ms\', sans-serif;\\\">We hope that this additional detail provides a deeper understanding of what Lakme stands for and what our future aspirations are. We are passionate about empowering women and celebrating their natural beauty, and we look forward to continuing to do so for many years to come.<\\/span><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><\\/div><div class=\\\"flex justify-between\\\"><div class=\\\"text-gray-400 flex self-end lg:self-center justify-center mt-2 gap-3 md:gap-4 lg:gap-1 lg:absolute lg:top-0 lg:translate-x-full lg:right-0 lg:mt-0 lg:pl-2 visible\\\" style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div><\\/div><\\/div><\\/div><\\/div>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
