oboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #f7f7f8;\">Our Values: At Lakme, we value innovation, quality, diversity, and sustainability. We are always exploring new and innovative ways to create products that cater to the diverse needs of women in India. We are committed to using only the finest and most sustainable ingredients in our products to ensure that we leave the smallest possible carbon footprint. We celebrate diversity and inclusivity in everything we do, and strive to create a welcoming and empowering environment for all our employees, customers, and partners.</p><p style=\"border-style: solid; border-color: #d9d9e3; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 1.25em; color: #374151; font-family: Shne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #f7f7f8;\">Our Legacy: Lakme\'s legacy is one of innovation and excellence. Over the past 50 years, we have introduced numerous groundbreaking products and technologies that have revolutionized the beauty industry in India. Our pioneering spirit has made us one of the most trusted and well-loved beauty brands in the country, and we are proud to have played a part in empowering millions of women across India.</p><p style=\"border-style: solid; border-color: #d9d9e3; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 1.25em; color: #374151; font-family: Shne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #f7f7f8;\">Our Team: Our team at Lakme is made up of some of the most talented and passionate professionals in the beauty industry. From product development to marketing, sales to customer service, every member of our team is dedicated to delivering the best possible beauty experience to our customers. We believe in nurturing talent and providing opportunities for growth and development, and are proud to have a diverse and inclusive team that reflects the values and aspirations of our brand.</p><p style=\"border-style: solid; border-color: #d9d9e3; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #374151; font-family: Shne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #f7f7f8;\">Thank you for taking the time to learn more about Lakme. We hope that our passion for beauty and commitment to excellence comes through in everything we do, and that you will join us on our journey to empower women and celebrate the beauty of diversity in India.</p>		\n			<style>/*! elementor - v3.11.5 - 14-03-2023 */\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}</style>												<img width=\"259\" height=\"194\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/lkm.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n															<img width=\"337\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/lk2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>Welcome to Lakme, a leading cosmetics brand in India that has been empowering women for over 50 years. Our journey began in 1952, when we launched the first-ever beauty salon in India, and since then, we have been committed to delivering high-quality and innovative beauty products that enhance the natural beauty of women.<br>At Lakme, we believe that beauty is not just about external appearances, but also about inner confidence and self-esteem. Our products are designed to help women feel confident and beautiful from within, by enhancing their natural features and complementing their unique personalities<br></p>		\n															<img width=\"300\" height=\"168\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/css.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n															<img width=\"340\" height=\"148\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ssss.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>From skincare to makeup, haircare to fragrances, our products are crafted using the latest technologies and the finest ingredients, to provide the best possible results for our customers. Our product range caters to every skin type, age, and occasion, and is constantly evolving to meet the ever-changing needs of women.<br /><br /></p><p>We are also committed to sustainability and social responsibility, and have implemented various initiatives to reduce our carbon footprint and support the communities we operate in. We believe in giving back to society and have partnered with various organizations to promote education, health, and environmental awareness.<br />Thank you for choosing Lakme as your beauty partner. We are dedicated to providing you with the best possible beauty experience and look forward to continuing to empower women for many more years to come.</p>		\n															<img width=\"266\" height=\"189\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/1342w34r5.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		Our Product Range: At Lakme, we offer a wide range of beauty products that cater to every skin type, age, and occasion. Our skincare range includes products for cleansing, toning, moisturizing, and treating various skin concerns, such as acne, dark spots, and aging. Our makeup range includes products for face, eyes, lips, and nails, and is designed to enhance and highlight the natural features of every woman. We also offer arange of haircare products, including shampoos, conditioners, and styling products, as well as fragrances that cater to every mood and personality.                                                                                                       \