(72, 1, '2023-03-26 13:33:55', '2023-03-26 13:33:55', '<style>/*! elementor - v3.11.5 - 14-03-2023 */\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}</style>												<img width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/12345.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>Nehru quickly approached industrialist Jehangir Ratanji Dadabhoy Tata for a solution and Lakm was introduced as Indias first homegrown cosmetics brand in 1952. It was a<a href=\"https://www.tatacentralarchives.com/tata-legacy/lakmes-history.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">subsidiary</a>of Tata Oil Mills, a company originally tasked with crushing copra for exporting coconut oil.</p>\n<p>The name Lakme is a French word for goddess Lakshmi, known for her beauty in mythology. This was suggested by the brands French collaborators, Robert Piguet and Renoir. Lakme was a popular opera in France by Lo Delibes, named after its protagonist who was inspired by the Indian goddess.</p>\n<p>Lakme was groundbreaking for the Indian market because it offered cosmetics suitable for Indian skin types, for which extensive research was<a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/349463522_A_Comprehensive_Analysis_of_Top_Indian_Cosmetic_Company_LAKME\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">carried out</a>.The brand got a<a href=\"https://corporatecitizen.in/v2-issue3/corporate-history-lakme-was-nehrus-idea.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">makeover</a>when Dadabhoys Swiss wife Simone Tata took over as its managing director in 1961. From pricing of products to the brands positioning, she made it a household name. Simone became the companys chairperson in 1982.<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Screenshot-from-2023-03-26-18-03-11.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" /></p>\n<p>Go-to brand</p>\n<p>I never knew Lakm was an Indian brand. I always thought it was European. And it was affordable too, so I always liked to buy them during my college days. But the reason for my preference was also because it was everywhere. It was advertised in the newspapers, TV and all my favorite actors were in it. I still use some of its products, said 44-year old Seema Rana, a teacher at a Delhi school.</p>\n<p>Dolly Sharma, also a Delhi resident, had similar reasons for liking Lakm products over others.</p>\n<p>My husband runs a pharmacy. Lakm brings us the most revenue because it is the preferred choice of customers. Personally, I have known about the brand for the longest time. It was the only makeup brand I knew that was used by people around memy mother and elder sister. So when it came for my time to choose a brand for myself, it was quite straightforward and simple, she said.</p>\n<p></p><p>At Lakm Salon, with over 35 years of experience, and a footprint of over 400+ Lakm Salons in 125 cities across the length and breadth of the country, we have developed a deep understanding of the beauty industry, its professionals and the skills needed to make a mark. More than 280 entrepreneurs have partnered with Lakm Lever as franchisees to own and operate Lakm Salons across the country</p>		\n															<img width=\"430\" height=\"373\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Screenshot-from-2023-03-26-18-34-32.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>In 1996, Lakm was captured in an image for the first time. The first snapshot to mark the beginning of the brand\'s journey.</p>\nLakm wins its first European distribution agreements at the COSMOPROF WORLDWIDE fair in Bologna.\nThe brand wins its first distribution agreements in Taiwan, Hong Kong, Malaysia and Australia at the COSMOPROF ASIA fair.\nRelaunching of Collage permanent coloring and expansion of the collections shades.\n2002\n\n<a title=\"2002\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-6.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-6.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-6.jpg 200w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-6-150x150.jpg 150w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-6-180x180.jpg 180w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-6-100x100.jpg 100w\" alt=\"Lakme 2002\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a>\nInauguration of the companys new facilities in Sant Just Desvern.\n2003\n\n<a title=\"2003\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-7.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-7.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" alt=\"Lakme 2003\" width=\"202\" height=\"254\" /></a>\nLakm achieves its first distributors in North America at the COSMORPROF NORTH AMERICA fair.\n2004\n\n<a title=\"2004\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-8.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-8.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-8.jpg 200w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-8-150x150.jpg 150w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-8-180x180.jpg 180w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-8-100x100.jpg 100w\" alt=\"Lakme 2004\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a>\nThe brand is now present in more than 65 countries and Lakm becomes and international hairdressing hub.\n2006\n\n<a title=\"2006\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-9.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-9.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-9.jpg 200w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-9-150x150.jpg 150w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-9-180x180.jpg 180w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-9-100x100.jpg 100w\" alt=\"Lakme 2006\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a>\nReformulation of the ammonia-free, semi-permanent Gloss coloring collection and launching of new shades.\n2007\n\n<a title=\"2007\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-10.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-10.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-10.jpg 200w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-10-150x150.jpg 150w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-10-180x180.jpg 180w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-10-100x100.jpg 100w\" alt=\"Lakme 2007\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a>\nRelaunching of k.therapy, the wellness and health treatment for hair and scalp.\n2008\n\n<a title=\"2008\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-11.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-11.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-11.jpg 200w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-11-150x150.jpg 150w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-11-180x180.jpg 180w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-11-100x100.jpg 100w\" alt=\"Lakme 2008\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a>\nReformulation of k.style, the line of finishing products that create lasting volume, shine, texture and extreme finishes.\n2009\n\n<img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"457\" height=\"172\" />\n2010\n\n<a title=\"2010\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-13.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-13.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" alt=\"Lakme 2010\" width=\"200\" height=\"280\" /></a>\nRelaunching TEKNIA, Lakms high-tech line designed to hydrate and care for all hair types\n2012\n\n<a title=\"2012\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-14.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-14.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-14.jpg 200w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-14-150x150.jpg 150w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-14-180x180.jpg 180w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-14-100x100.jpg 100w\" alt=\"Lakme 2012\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a>\nLaunching of Collage+, permanent coloring that provides maximum color intensity and gray coverage.\n2013\n\n<a title=\"2013\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-15.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-15.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-15.jpg 200w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-15-174x300.jpg 174w\" alt=\"Lakme 2013\" width=\"200\" height=\"344\" /></a>\nLaunching of CHROMA, Lakms ammonia-free permanent coloring.\n2014\n\n<a title=\"2014\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-16.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-16.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-16.jpg 200w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-16-150x150.jpg 150w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-16-180x180.jpg 180w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/timeline-16-100x100.jpg 100w\" alt=\"Lakme 2014\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a>\nLaunching of k.style COOL, the trendiest finishing products to create unique looks.\n2015\n\n<img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/timeline-17b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"242\" />Inauguration of the companys new facilities.\n2016\n\n<a title=\"2016\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/timeline-18_2.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/timeline-18_2.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" alt=\"2016\" width=\"184\" height=\"215\" /></a>\n<p>Lakm defies the passage of time with<b>i.plex</b>: an anti-aging treatment that fights the aging process of hair.</p>\n2017\n\n<a title=\"2017\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/timeline-19_2.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/timeline-19_2.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" alt=\"2017\" width=\"188\" height=\"139\" /></a>\n<p>The most spectacular blondes with<b>k.blonde</b>: k.blonde Bleaching Clay and k.blonde Bleaching cream ammonia-free make it possible to customize the most desired shades of blonde.</p>\n2018\n\n<a title=\"2018\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/timeline-20.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/timeline-20.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" alt=\"2018\" width=\"184\" height=\"241\" /></a>\nCHROMA, reinventing color. It is formulated with the exclusive OF5 molecule, a revolutionary technology in hair coloring. The first molecule capable of delaying the oxidation of dyes.\n<a title=\"2018\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/timeline-21.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/timeline-21.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" alt=\"2018\" width=\"168\" height=\"201\" /></a>\nAURA, the first biotechnological hair treatment formulated with organic ingredients that straightens and softens the hair fiber and eliminates frizz.\n2019\n\n<a title=\"2019\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/timeline-22-1.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/timeline-22-1.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/timeline-22-1.jpg 300w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/timeline-22-1-215x300.jpg 215w\" alt=\"2019\" width=\"300\" height=\"419\" /></a>\nTEKNIA is the fusion of experience, innovation and inspiration: the best beauty ritual for nourished, healthy and eternally beautiful hair.\n2021\n\n<a title=\"2021\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/reshaping-color.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/reshaping-color.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/reshaping-color.jpg 900w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/reshaping-color-300x250.jpg 300w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/reshaping-color-768x640.jpg 768w\" alt=\"2021\" width=\"525\" height=\"438\" /></a>\nLakm creates the integrated color system. Collage is evolving, but its flagship formula remain intact. Gloss, the ammonia-free, demipermanent, strengthens haircare and exclusively partners with Collage to achieve an integrated Lakm color system.\n2022\n\n<a title=\"2022\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-1024x1024.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-150x150.jpg 150w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-300x300.jpg 300w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-768x768.jpg 768w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-250x250.jpg 250w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-180x180.jpg 180w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-600x600.jpg 600w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/TK-SCALP-RELIEF_BODEGON-RGB-100x100.jpg 100w\" alt=\"2022\" width=\"525\" height=\"525\" /></a>\n<p>LAKM is expanding the universe of TEKNIA.</p>\n<p><b>TEKNIA SCALP CARE</b>is an avant-garde line of products designed to treat the root problem in order to protect, soothe, nourish, and rebalance the scalp.</p>\n2023\n\n<a title=\"2023\" href=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB.png\"><img src=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-1024x1024.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-150x150.png 150w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-300x300.png 300w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-768x768.png 768w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-250x250.png 250w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-180x180.png 180w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-600x600.png 600w, https://lakme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/K20_BODEGON-v02-RGB-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"2023\" width=\"525\" height=\"525\" /></a>\n<strong>k.blonde</strong>, \"The ultimate protection for blondes\" and<strong>K2.0</strong>, \"At the top of restoring hair\". Two launches that, combined, achieve optimum performance.\n\n', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-03-26 13:33:55', '2023-03-26 13:33:55', '', 15, 'http://localhost/wordpress1/wordpress/?p=72', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
