(92, 1, '2023-03-26 14:07:23', '2023-03-26 14:07:23', '<style>/*! elementor - v3.11.5 - 14-03-2023 */<br />\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}</style>												<img width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/12345.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n\nNehru quickly approached industrialist Jehangir Ratanji Dadabhoy Tata for a solution and Lakm was introduced as Indias first homegrown cosmetics brand in 1952. It was a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tatacentralarchives.com/tata-legacy/lakmes-history.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">subsidiary</a>&nbsp;of Tata Oil Mills, a company originally tasked with crushing copra for exporting coconut oil.\n\nThe name Lakme is a French word for goddess Lakshmi, known for her beauty in mythology. This was suggested by the brands French collaborators, Robert Piguet and Renoir. Lakme was a popular opera in France by Lo Delibes, named after its protagonist who was inspired by the Indian goddess.\n\nLakme was groundbreaking for the Indian market because it offered cosmetics suitable for Indian skin types, for which extensive research was&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/349463522_A_Comprehensive_Analysis_of_Top_Indian_Cosmetic_Company_LAKME\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">carried out</a>.The brand got a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://corporatecitizen.in/v2-issue3/corporate-history-lakme-was-nehrus-idea.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">makeover</a>&nbsp;when Dadabhoys Swiss wife Simone Tata took over as its managing director in 1961. From pricing of products to the brands positioning, she made it a household name. Simone became the companys chairperson in 1982.\n\n<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Screenshot-from-2023-03-26-18-03-11.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\">\n\nGo-to brand\n\nI never knew Lakm was an Indian brand. I always thought it was European. And it was affordable too, so I always liked to buy them during my college days. But the reason for my preference was also because it was everywhere. It was advertised in the newspapers, TV and all my favorite actors were in it. I still use some of its products, said 44-year old Seema Rana, a teacher at a Delhi school.\n\nDolly Sharma, also a Delhi resident, had similar reasons for liking Lakm products over others.\n\nMy husband runs a pharmacy. Lakm brings us the most revenue because it is the preferred choice of customers. Personally, I have known about the brand for the longest time. It was the only makeup brand I knew that was used by people around memy mother and elder sister. So when it came for my time to choose a brand for myself, it was quite straightforward and simple, she said.\n\nAt Lakm Salon, with over 35 years of experience, and a footprint of over 400+ Lakm Salons in 125 cities across the length and breadth of the country, we have developed a deep understanding of the beauty industry, its professionals and the skills needed to make a mark. More than 280 entrepreneurs have partnered with Lakm Lever as franchisees to own and operate Lakm Salons across the country\n\n<img width=\"430\" height=\"373\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Screenshot-from-2023-03-26-18-34-32.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n\nWelcome to Lakm, the beauty destination that inspires women all over the world to express their unique beauty. Our vision is to make every woman feel confident, radiant, and empowered through our premium beauty products.\n\nFor over 60 years, Lakm has been a trusted brand in the beauty industry, with a focus on innovation, quality, and inclusivity. Our collection of skincare, makeup, and haircare products is carefully curated to cater to all your beauty needs, from everyday essentials to special occasions.\n\nSkincare\n\nWe believe that beautiful makeup starts with healthy skin. That\'s why our skincare range is specially formulated to nourish, protect, and enhance your natural beauty. From gentle cleansers to hydrating moisturizers, our collection offers a variety of products for every skin type and concern. Our best-selling Absolute Perfect Radiance range is a fan-favorite, enriched with real gold micro particles to give you a radiant, glowing complexion.\n\nMakeup\n\nAt Lakm, we believe that makeup is an art form that can transform your look and boost your confidence. Our makeup range is designed to help you create any look you desire, whether it\'s a natural no-makeup makeup look or a bold, statement look. Our collection includes lipsticks, foundations, eyeshadows, mascaras, and more, in a variety of shades and finishes to suit every skin tone and type. Our signature product, the Lakm Absolute Argan Oil Serum Foundation, is a cult favorite, providing buildable coverage with a dewy finish that lasts all day.\n\nHaircare\n\nGood hair days are a must for any beauty routine, and our haircare range is specially formulated to help you achieve your dream hair. From nourishing shampoos and conditioners to hair masks and styling products, our collection offers everything you need to keep your locks healthy, shiny, and manageable. Our bestselling 9to5 Primer + Matte Lip Color is an everyday essential for any makeup bag.\n\nCollections\n\nLooking for inspiration? Our curated collections offer the latest beauty trends and timeless classics for every occasion. From bridal makeup to festive looks, our collections make it easy to find the perfect products to help you look and feel your best.\n\nShop with Confidence\n\nAt Lakm, we believe in providing our customers with the best shopping experience. Our online store is easy to use, and we offer a variety of payment options, including cash on delivery. Plus, we offer free shipping on all orders over [insert amount]. With our 100% satisfaction guarantee, you can shop with confidence knowing that you\'re getting the best products and service.\n\nJoin our Community\n\nConnect with other beauty enthusiasts and get inspired by our community of Lakm lovers. Follow us on social media to stay up to date on the latest trends, tips, and products. Join our loyalty program to earn rewards and exclusive offers.\n\nExperience the Beauty of Lakm\n\nAt Lakm, we believe that beauty is not just about looking good, but also feeling good. Our premium beauty products are designed to enhance your natural beauty and make you feel confident and empowered. Explore our collection today and discover the beauty of Lakm.\n\nIn 1996, Lakm was captured in an image for the first time. The first snapshot to mark the beginning of the brand\'s journey.\nLakm wins its first European distribution agreements at the COSMOPROF WORLDWIDE fair in Bologna.\nThe brand wins its first distribution agreements in Taiwan, Hong Kong, Malaysia and Australia at the COSMOPROF ASIA fair.\nRelaunching of Collage permanent coloring and expansion of the collections shades.\nInauguration of the companys new facilities in Sant Just Desvern.\nLakm achieves its first distributors in North America at the COSMORPROF NORTH AMERICA fair.\nThe brand is now present in more than 65 countries and Lakm becomes and international hairdressing hub.\nReformulation of the ammonia-free, semi-permanent Gloss coloring collection and launching of new shades.\nRelaunching of k.therapy, the wellness and health treatment for hair and scalp Reformulation of k.style, the line of finishing products that create lasting volume, shine, texture and extreme finishes. Relaunching TEKNIA, Lakms high-tech line designed to hydrate and care for all hair types\nLaunching of Collage+, permanent coloring that provides maximum color intensity and gray coverage.\nLaunching of CHROMA, Lakms ammonia-free permanent coloring.\nLaunching of k.style COOL, the trendiest finishing products to create unique looks.\nInauguration of the companys new facilities. Lakm defies the passage of time with i.plex: an anti-aging treatment that fights the aging process of hair. The most spectacular blondes with k.blonde: k.blonde Bleaching Clay and k.blonde Bleaching cream ammonia-free make it possible to customize the most desired shades of blonde.\nCHROMA, reinventing color. It is formulated with the exclusive OF5 molecule, a revolutionary technology in hair coloring. The first molecule capable of delaying the oxidation of dyes.\nAURA, the first biotechnological hair treatment formulated with organic ingredients that straightens and softens the hair fiber and eliminates frizz.\nTEKNIA is the fusion of experience, innovation and inspiration: the best beauty ritual for nourished, healthy and eternally beautiful hair.\nLakm creates the integrated color system. Collage is evolving, but its flagship formula remain intact. Gloss, the ammonia-free, demipermanent, strengthens haircare and exclusively partners with Collage to achieve an integrated Lakm color system.\nLAKM is expanding the universe of TEKNIA.\nTEKNIA SCALP CARE is an avant-garde line of products designed to treat the root problem in order to protect, soothe, nourish, and rebalance the scalp.\nk.blonde, \"The ultimate protection for blondes\" and K2.0, \"At the top of restoring hair\". Two launches that, combined, achieve optimum performance.\n\n<img width=\"225\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/123556.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n<img width=\"300\" height=\"168\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/35678.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n<img width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/12345-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '20