ore is easy to use, and we offer a variety of payment options, including cash on delivery. Plus, we offer free shipping on all orders over [insert amount]. With our 100% satisfaction guarantee, you can shop with confidence knowing that you\'re getting the best products and service.</p>\n<p>Join our Community</p>\n<p>Connect with other beauty enthusiasts and get inspired by our community of Lakm lovers. Follow us on social media to stay up to date on the latest trends, tips, and products. Join our loyalty program to earn rewards and exclusive offers.</p>\n<p>Experience the Beauty of Lakm</p>\n<p>At Lakm, we believe that beauty is not just about looking good, but also feeling good. Our premium beauty products are designed to enhance your natural beauty and make you feel confident and empowered. Explore our collection today and discover the beauty of Lakm.</p><p>In 1996, Lakm was captured in an image for the first time. The first snapshot to mark the beginning of the brand\'s journey.<br>Lakm wins its first European distribution agreements at the COSMOPROF WORLDWIDE fair in Bologna.<br>The brand wins its first distribution agreements in Taiwan, Hong Kong, Malaysia and Australia at the COSMOPROF ASIA fair.<br>Relaunching of Collage permanent coloring and expansion of the collections shades.<br>Inauguration of the companys new facilities in Sant Just Desvern.<br>Lakm achieves its first distributors in North America at the COSMORPROF NORTH AMERICA fair.<br>The brand is now present in more than 65 countries and Lakm becomes and international hairdressing hub.<br>Reformulation of the ammonia-free, semi-permanent Gloss coloring collection and launching of new shades.<br>Relaunching of k.therapy, the wellness and health treatment for hair and scalp Reformulation of k.style, the line of finishing products that create lasting volume, shine, texture and extreme finishes. Relaunching TEKNIA, Lakms high-tech line designed to hydrate and care for all hair types<br>Launching of Coll