age+, permanent coloring that provides maximum color intensity and gray coverage.<br>Launching of CHROMA, Lakms ammonia-free permanent coloring.<br>Launching of k.style COOL, the trendiest finishing products to create unique looks.<br>Inauguration of the companys new facilities. Lakm defies the passage of time with i.plex: an anti-aging treatment that fights the aging process of hair. The most spectacular blondes with k.blonde: k.blonde Bleaching Clay and k.blonde Bleaching cream ammonia-free make it possible to customize the most desired shades of blonde.<br>CHROMA, reinventing color. It is formulated with the exclusive OF5 molecule, a revolutionary technology in hair coloring. The first molecule capable of delaying the oxidation of dyes.<br>AURA, the first biotechnological hair treatment formulated with organic ingredients that straightens and softens the hair fiber and eliminates frizz.<br>TEKNIA is the fusion of experience, innovation and inspiration: the best beauty ritual for nourished, healthy and eternally beautiful hair.<br>Lakm creates the integrated color system. Collage is evolving, but its flagship formula remain intact. Gloss, the ammonia-free, demipermanent, strengthens haircare and exclusively partners with Collage to achieve an integrated Lakm color system.<br>LAKM is expanding the universe of TEKNIA.<br>TEKNIA SCALP CARE is an avant-garde line of products designed to treat the root problem in order to protect, soothe, nourish, and rebalance the scalp.<br>k.blonde, \"The ultimate protection for blondes\" and K2.0, \"At the top of restoring hair\". Two launches that, combined, achieve optimum performance.</p>		\n															<img width=\"225\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/123556.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n															<img width=\"300\" height=\"168\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/35678.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />				